> **Validate trading approaches with historical data before live deployment**

![Backtest Results Example](backtest_results.png)

## âœ¨ Key Features

| Component | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Delta Trading Algorithm** | Robust backtester with Kelly criterion position sizing |
| **Trend Following Strategy**| MA-based with configurable stop-loss/take-profit |
| **VWAP Strategies** | Basic and enhanced versions with RSI/ATR filtering |
| **Multi-Indicator Strategy**| Combines Supertrend, MACD, and VWAP |
| **Data Integration** | Historical OHLCV from multiple exchanges |
| **Visual Analytics** | Interactive plots & performance metrics |

